            "creation_date": 1468306564,
            "body": "<p>Eclipse WTP's JSP Editor doesn't offer to do this completely automatically, but it can provide content assist for the taglib directive and its attribute values based on what it finds. Proposals for the prefix are based on the URI value.<\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/R6SEy.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/R6SEy.png\" alt=\"Proposals for the URI value\"><\/a><\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 38321937,
            "question_id": 38321669
        },
